div.p: The library Fairris is built with is called Yew and implements the react model. In Yew, the Components are not members of the parent component. Instead, the relationship is similar to the HTML DOM model, and is also represented this way in code.
Agents make it easier to manage state and do certain tasks with application-wide impact.
Components and Agents communicate by sending messages the receiver component has defined for itself.
